    {
      "title": "[负面] Very decent game that I can't recommend at the cur...",
      "summary": "Very decent game that I can't recommend at the current time.\nEvery stage is pretty much a mini roguelite where you collect relics and power up your party's cards, and then you fight the final boss.\nThe different factions and synergies were pretty interesting.\nThere even is a pvp mode where each character has a different card for this mode.\nThe devs are also pretty generous with pulls.\n\nAs for the negative points, only the prologue has any voice acting, aside from combat.\nThe story was unreadable to me, because the text were very obviously machine-translated and did not make any sense.\nThe skill cards and mechanics are also machine translated and were inconsistent in some places.\nI couldn't get invested in the story or character, since I had no idea what was going on, and the bosses were starting to get unreasonably hard, so I just dipped, would not recommend unless they actually get human translation for everything.",
      "source": "steam_review",
      "time": "2026-07-06T20:05:17+00:00",
      "url": "https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561198803467446/recommended/3052450",
